00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,880
You can hand him over to the police.

279
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,760
But I have to make them pay.

280
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:55,440
And I'll do it myself.

281
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:18,650
♪ Mist coils around the sleeping forest ♪

282
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:22,300
♪ Memories scattered
through cracks of darkness ♪

283
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:26,150
♪ How to escape this real-feeling dream ♪

284
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:32,960
♪ Lies reflect in water's gleam ♪

285
00:13:33,190 --> 00:13:36,520
♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

286
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:40,080
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

287
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:49,470
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

288
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:53,496
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

289
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:57,106
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

290
00:13:57,130 --> 00:14:00,060
♪ Burn like fire ♪

291
00:14:00,090 --> 00:14:03,500
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

292
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:07,600
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

293
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:10,326
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

294
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:13,490
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

295
00:14:13,770 --> 00:14:17,280
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

296
00:14:17,350 --> 00:14:23,810
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

297
00:14:24,460 --> 00:14:27,776
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

298
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:31,330
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

299
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:38,080
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

300
00:14:38,490 --> 00:14:40,340
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

